      "created_at": "2016-10-06T02:02:32.617Z",
      "cooked": "<p>U dalshin portokallet nga syte, mos tu them ate tjetren u thafshin duart…<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/smiley.png?v=5\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smiley:\"></p>",
