      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/50afbb/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2016-10-06T03:09:11.744Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Prane gjykates thote. Mire ua kane bo, drejtesia e korruptuar s’meriton agrume. Reforma ne drejtesi i ka keto, e ka thone dhe Lu-ja, rrup sup do ia boj korruptacjas.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
